g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9c5a7e43d0fec6d001e252d898b62187835c89","tid":618379,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T18:21:21.000Z","msg":"呢隻玩過，之後覺得漫畫版做基礎果隻road to survival 好玩d, 不過都就棄坑"},{"pid":"85ea08359e274045ba9f19fdda700d0651d0e950","tid":618379,"uid":3779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T21:34:14.000Z","msg":"岩岩出個陣瘋狂玩，之後棄左<br />\n近排又玩返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0956c9dacf9b69b4c55de724a8bb92f06a14cd","tid":618379,"uid":19643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T07:41:20.000Z","msg":"幾好玩"},{"pid":"9d961dc050e0d15c6bb9e83965b5df6ddb2665d3","tid":618379,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T22:14:50.000Z","msg":"唔錯"},{"pid":"9f14ba76d3caf9307c6b43be827cb9116627c2da","tid":618379,"uid":190665,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T17:30:50.000Z","msg":"有無tg grp傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啱啱玩"},{"pid":"3d0c2c0fead5f3f6b82067b0f20740e654a1751e","tid":618379,"uid":12594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T19:04:54.000Z","msg":"hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}